    Library Collections
     Standards [menuiconred.gif]

   Research Library
       FULL TEXT     FAQ

   Code of Federal Regulations
          From the U.S. House of Representatives

   DOE Orders and Directives
          Includes the Secretary of Energy Notices and the Albuquerque
          Area Office Notices.

   Federal Register
          Full text with a searchable interface covering 1994-present.

   IHS Specs & Standards new icon
          Full text of ANSI A-Z, ANS, ASCE, ASHRAE, ASME and the Boiler
          &Pressure Vessel Code, ASQ, ASTM, AWS, DOD Military Specs and
          Standards including historical, DOD Adopted Industry Standards,
          ISA, ISO Quality, NEMA, NFPA, SMACNA, and UL. Includes
          searchable index to industry standards.

   LANL Administrative Manual
          LANL access only.

   Science Server
          Contains full text of IEEE standards. LANL access only.

   UC-DOE Contract

