    INDEXES & ABSTRACTS

   ANSI Catalog
          Searchable database of over 11,000 approved American National
          Standards.

   ASTM Standards
          Search for an individual ASTM standard.

   BIPM key comparison database
          A comparision of national measurement standards.

   Document Center
          A commercial service with a searchable interface to their
          inventory of standards. Includes DOD Index of Specifications &
          Standards, US Industry Standards, NISO, and some ISO Standards.

   DODISS
          Department of Defense Index of Specifications and Standards.

   DODSPS
          Department of Defense Single Point Stock for Military
          Specifications, Standards and Related Publications-Assist Quick
          Search.

   DOE Acquisition Regulations (DEAR)
          DOE Technical Standards

   IEEE Standards Catalog
          Search for an individual IEEE standard.

   International Organization for Standardization (ISO)
          ISO Catalogue searchable by keywords or ISO reference number.
          Index and ordering information for standards, not full-text of
          standards themselves. Includes lists of ISO member and
          committees.

   MSDS Databases
          MSDS at Oxford University
          OHS MSDS Reference Database

   NSSN Basic Search
          Contains over 100,000 references to approved standards from more
          than 600 developers world wide,including ANSI, private standards
          organizations, government agencies, DOD, and international
          organizations.
